{"infos":[{"key":"QE_BGN_01","value":"事先確認敵人的<color=#00ffff>攻擊類型耐性</color>，<br>更有效率地給予其傷害吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_02","value":"連續以同樣<color=#00ffff>攻擊類型</color><color=#00ffff>攻擊</color>敵人，<br>發動<color=#00ffff>連擊</color>吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_03","value":"<color=#00ffff>操作鏡頭</color>找尋敵人吧。使用<br><color=#00ffff>詠唱能力</color>的基本原則是選擇<color=#00ffff>「兵員」</color>。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_04","value":"試著使用消耗<color=#00ffff>TP</color>的能力、<br>消耗<color=#00ffff>AP</color>的能力，<br>還有<color=#00ffff>極限技</color>吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_05","value":"兵員之間有<color=#00ffff>屬性</color><color=#00ffff>相剋</color>，<br>事先確認<color=#00ffff>彼此的屬性</color>後再<color=#00ffff>攻擊</color>吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_06","value":"<color=#00ffff>能力</color>有<color=#00ffff>屬性</color>，<br><color=#00ffff>兵員</color>則有<color=#00ffff>屬性耐性</color>，<br>事先確認敵人的屬性耐性後再攻擊吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_07","value":"以<color=#00ffff>同屬性</color>的<color=#00ffff>能力</color><color=#00ffff>連續攻擊</color>敵人，<br>來發動<color=#00ffff>屬性連擊</color>吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_08","value":"<color=#00ffff>瑪雪莉</color>的<color=#00ffff>「復原」</color>是用來<color=#00ffff>恢復</color><color=#00ffff>異常狀態</color>，<br>而<color=#00ffff>「反制災禍」</color>是用來<color=#00ffff>預防</color><color=#00ffff>異常狀態</color>。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_09","value":"確認<color=#00ffff>敵人</color>的<color=#00ffff>異常狀態耐性</color>，<br>使用<color=#00ffff>耐性</color><color=#00ffff>較低的</color>異常狀態吧。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_10","value":"弓有著從<color=#00ffff>較高的地方</color>射出箭，<br><color=#00ffff>射程就會延長</color><br>的特性。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_11","value":"<color=#00ffff>敏捷</color>越高<color=#00ffff>越能儘早</color>行動，<br><color=#00ffff>決定行動</color>後，會<color=#00ffff>更快輪到</color>下個<color=#00ffff>行動</color>。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_12","value":"<color=#00ffff>HP0</color>會陷入<color=#00ffff>無法戰鬥的狀態</color>並開始倒數計時。<br><color=#00ffff>倒數計時為0</color>便會從戰場上<color=#00ffff>消失</color>。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_13","value":"<color=#00ffff>敵人</color>陷入<color=#00ffff>無法戰鬥</color>狀態時，會<color=#00ffff>掉落道具</color>，<br><color=#00ffff>兵員</color><color=#00ffff>消失</color>後會產生<color=#00ffff>水晶</color>。"},{"key":"QE_BGN_14","value":"積蓄<color=#00ffff>召喚槽</color>，<br>發動強力的<color=#00ffff>召喚魔法</color>吧。"}]}